<body>

<div class="mdl-layout mdl-js-layout mdl-layout--fixed-header mdl-layout--fixed-drawer">
    <header class="mdl-layout__header mdl-color--indigo">
        <div class="mdl-layout__header-row">
            <div class="mdl-layout-spacer">
            </div>
            <a href="client" class="mdl-button mdl-color--pink mdl-color-text--white">Login</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <aside class="mdl-layout__drawer">
        <ul class="mdl-list">
            <li class="mdl-list__item"><a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/readerself">Download</a></li>
            <li class="mdl-list__item"><a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/readerself/readerself/issues">Support</a></li>
            <li class="mdl-list__item"><a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/readerself/readerself/archive/master.zip">Download</a></li>
            <li class="mdl-list__item"><a target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/readerself">Community</a></li>
        </ul>
    </aside>

    <main class="mdl-layout__content mdl-color--grey-100">
        <div class="mdl-snackbar mdl-js-snackbar">
            <div class="mdl-snackbar__text"></div>
            <button type="button" class="mdl-snackbar__action"></button>
        </div>

        <div class="mdl-grid" id="top">
            <div class="mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp mdl-color--white mdl-cell mdl-cell--12-col">
                <div class="mdl-card__title">
                    <h1 class="mdl-card__title-text">
                        Reader Self - Self-hosted rss reader
                    </h1>
                    <div class="mdl-card__subtitle-text">
                        Import OPML - Responsive desktop, tablet and mobile - Main keyboard shortcuts from Google Reader - Automatic tags - Shared items with public feed
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp mdl-color--white mdl-cell mdl-cell--6-col mdl-cell--12-col-tablet mdl-cell--12-col-phone">
                <div class="mdl-card__title">
                    <h1 class="mdl-card__title-text">
                        Features
                    </h1>
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="api/documentation">API server (Symfony)</a>, with provided html5 client</li>
                        <li>Built-in authentication</li>
                        <li>Responsive desktop, tablet and mobile</li>
                        <li>Multilingual (English and French)</li>
                        <li>Get feed from Facebook Pages</li>
                        <li>Automatic tags from item categories</li>
                        <li>List items by feed</li>
                        <li>List items by tag</li>
                        <li>List items by author</li>
                        <li>Main keyboard shortcuts from Google Reader</li>
                        <li>Get enclosures (image, audio and video)</li>
                        <li>Keep only iframes from Dailymotion, Vimeo and Youtube</li>
                        <li>Starred items</li>
                        <li>Sync starred items with Pinboard</li>
                        <li>Multi-users</li>
                        <li>Share on Facebook, Google+, LinkedIn, Twitter ...</li>
                        <li>Elastic search integration (feeds, items and categories)</li>
                        <li>Adaptive crawl by feed (older than 96 hours, next crawl in 12 hours / older than 48 hours, next crawl in 6 hours / older than 24 hours, next crawl in 3 hours)</li>
                        <li>Expand / Collapse items</li>
                        <li>TODO Text direction according to feed language (left to right / right to left)</li>
                        <li>TODO Send article to Evernote</li>
                        <li>TODO Add a feed or website url (feed detection)</li>
                        <li>TODO Import and export OPML</li>
                        <li>TODO Live unread counter in title bar / tab</li>
                        <li>TODO Share by email</li>
                        <li>TODO Full content from Readability</li>
                        <li>TODO Get unread items notification from your Reader Self installation (Chrome Web Store / Safari direct download / Opera direct download)</li>
                        <li>TODO Detect feeds in current page and get direct links to subscribe (Chrome Web Store)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp mdl-color--white mdl-cell mdl-cell--6-col mdl-cell--12-col-tablet mdl-cell--12-col-phone">
                <div class="mdl-card__title">
                    <h1 class="mdl-card__title-text">
                        Shortcuts
                    </h1>
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">
                    <ul>
                        <li>r: reload</li>
                        <li>t: expand / collapse all items</li>
                        <li>a: add a subscription</li>
                        <li>k or p or shift + space: up / previous item</li>
                        <li>j or n or space: down / next item</li>
                        <li>g then a: go to all items</li>
                        <li>g then u: go to unread items</li>
                        <li>g then s: go to starred items</li>
                        <li>shift + a: mark all as read</li>
                        <li>v: view original from selected item</li>
                        <li>m: read / unread selected item</li>
                        <li>s: star / unstar selected item</li>
                        <li>o or enter: expand / collapse selected item</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp mdl-color--white mdl-cell mdl-cell--12-col">
                <div class="mdl-card__title">
                    <h1 class="mdl-card__title-text">
                        Screenshots
                    </h1>
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">
                    <p>
                        <a href="screenshot.png" target="_blank"><img src="screenshot.png" alt=""></a>
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <a href="add-to-homescreen.png" target="_blank"><img src="add-to-homescreen.png" alt=""></a>
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <a href="notification.png" target="_blank"><img src="notification.png" alt=""></a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</div>

